tags.name: a11y-compare-image
tags.description:
`a11y-compare-image`
Layers images over each other with a slider interface to compare them

Attributes:

  * `active-layer` {`number`} - 

  * `__lower` {`string`} - 

  * `__upper` {`string`} - 

  * `opacity` {`boolean`} - mode for the slider: wipe

  * `position` {`number`} - 

  * `__markers` {`any[]`} - 

  * `accent-color` {`string`} - a selected accent-"color": grey, red, pink, purple, etc.

  * `dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

Properties:

  * `activeLayer` {`number`} -

  * `dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

  * `colors` -
